{"tid":383988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指抄國歌 黎明：我擺明玩國歌","createTime":"2017-09-02T02:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T07:22:08.000Z","uid":19552,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97b5867139ba71212014bd5ebd25498844213f45","tid":383988,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"《全日愛》被收錄於黎明的大碟《北京站》，於2000年發行，由林夕作詞、雷頌德作由及編曲。歌曲一開始就重覆了兩次國歌的首數個拍子，雷頌德於2014年10月接受電台訪問時，曾經以《全日愛》回應指摘他抄歌的問題，當時他公開說：「話我抄國歌，我係擺到明玩國歌嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，黎明於2000年推出有國歌元素版本的《全日愛》，的確惹來「玩國歌」的質疑，據當時傳媒報道，唱片公司稱雖然沒有收到投訴，但會在台灣及內地推出另一版本、即沒有國歌的《全日愛》。"},{"pid":"32e1dbadebbbb445a672d35741360d36a0fbdd08","tid":383988,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"玩命 你老友成龍都俾人捉個仔"},{"pid":"e4dae4c26faa24c1f2f37fd403375676fa873982","tid":383988,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b5093824aad8463b77cf57380e55345d3a9bfea","tid":383988,"uid":29804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"雷頌德回應<br />\n唔係黎明"},{"pid":"e4e3abef5b0bbe7c9aee357145706aedf965ade8","tid":383988,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5b324ec4ffc7305ea78cbfde03f414f9ceba47","tid":383988,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雷頌德回應<br />\n唔係黎明</blockquote><br />\nSor"},{"pid":"342d729fe6016b2244364949da7d4849f16daf33","tid":383988,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/l